kieker.monitoring.core.controller

Annotation Type ReceiveUnfilteredConfiguration


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Inherited
public @interface ReceiveUnfilteredConfiguration
    Using this annotation, controllers can request to receive an unfiltered configuration instance. By default, controllers receive only the configuration parameters starting with their class name.
    Since:
    1.13
    Author:
    Holger Knoche
